      • openConfirm

        public static boolean openConfirm(org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Shell parent,
                  java.lang.String title,
                  java.lang.String message,
                  java.lang.String[] buttons)
        Convenience method to open a simple confirm (OK/Cancel) dialog.
        Parameters:
        parent - the parent shell of the dialog, or null if none
        title - the dialog's title, or null if none
        message - the message
        Returns:
        true if the user presses the OK button, false otherwise

      • openSelectDialog

        public static java.lang.String openSelectDialog(org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Shell parentShell,
                                java.lang.String title,
                                java.lang.String message,
                                java.lang.String[] buttons,
                                org.eclipse.swt.graphics.Image selectionListImage,
                                java.util.List<java.lang.String> elementList)
        Convenience method to open a select dialog.
        Parameters:
        parentShell - the parent shell of the dialog, or null if none
        title - the dialog's title, or null if none
        message - the message
        buttons - the labels of the buttons to appear in the button bar
        classList - the list of elements have to be displayed in the selection list
        Returns:
        selected text if the user presses the OK button, null otherwise
